lyrics:
(Verse)
In my room, with the lights turned low,
Playing games, in the virtual glow.
With a controller in my hand, I'm the king,
Beating levels, doing my thing.

(Chorus)
Then I take a break, head on down to Wendy's way,
Ordering a burger, fries — oh, what a play!
Eating to the beat, as my console softly hums,
Doo-wop, doo-wah, it's all fun and games 'til the night becomes.
